  "body": "Hi I have one question.\r\n\r\nI would like to build an erigon node and allow rpc requests to come through from the outside, how do I set this up?\r\n\r\nI have been running \"v2.38.1\" and it worked fine, but with the new version \"v2.42.0\", I get a ConnectionError when accessing from the outside and access fails.\r\n\r\nHere is an excerpt from the docker-compose configuration file that starts erigon.\r\n\r\n```\r\n  erigon:\r\n    container_name: erigon\r\n    image: thorax/erigon:${ERIGON_VERSION:-v2.42.0}\r\n    restart: unless-stopped\r\n    volumes:\r\n      - /data:/data\r\n    ports:\r\n      - \"8545:8545\" # RPC API (TCP)\r\n      - \"8551:8551\" # Engine API (TCP)\r\n      - \"30303:30303\" # P2P (TCP)\r\n    logging:\r\n      driver: \"json-file\"\r\n      options:\r\n        max-size: \"1g\"\r\n        max-file: \"5\"\r\n    command:\r\n      - \"--datadir=/data/erigon\" \r\n      # - \"--datadir=/home/erigon/.local/share/erigon\" \r\n      - \"--metrics\" \r\n      - \"--metrics.addr=0.0.0.0\"\r\n      - \"--metrics.port=6060\" \r\n      - \"--private.api.addr=0.0.0.0:9090\" \r\n      - \"--pprof\"\r\n      - \"--pprof.addr=0.0.0.0\" \r\n      - \"--pprof.port=6061\"\r\n      - \"--http\"\r\n      - \"--http.addr=0.0.0.0\" \r\n      - \"--http.vhosts=*\" \r\n      - \"--http.corsdomain=*\" \r\n      - \"--http.api=eth,debug,net,trace,erigon,engine\"\r\n      - \"--ws\"\r\n      - \"--rpc.batch.concurrency=20000\"\r\n      - \"--rpc.batch.limit=50000\"\r\n      - \"--db.read.concurrency=50000\"\r\n      - \"--authrpc.jwtsecret=/data/jwt.hex\"\r\n      - \"--authrpc.addr=0.0.0.0\"\r\n      - \"--authrpc.vhosts=*\"\r\n    expose:\r\n      - 8545\r\n```\r\n\r\nI don't know if this is related, but in \"v2.38.1\" and \"v2.42.0\", the log when the RPC server starts was changed as follows.\r\n(The URL has changed from \"0.0.0.0.0\" to \"[::]\")\r\n```\r\n# v2.38.1\r\n[INFO] [04-09|03:24:55.030] HTTP endpoint opened for Engine API      url=0.0.0.0:8551 ws=true ws.compression=true\r\n[INFO] [04-09|03:24:55.030] HTTP endpoint opened                     url=0.0.0.0:8545 ws=true ws.compression=true grpc=false\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n# v2.42.0\r\n[INFO] [04-12|07:05:19.680] HTTP endpoint opened for Engine API      url=[::]:8551 ws=true ws.compression=true\r\n[INFO] [04-12|07:05:19.681] HTTP endpoint opened                     url=[::]:8545 ws=true ws.compression=true grpc=false\r\n```\r\n",
